desc: TSTCM is a reputable leader in TCM and Acupuncture education with a solid history of 25 years in Canada. Proven track records of high pass rate for registration examinations in Canada (Pan-Canadian Examinations) and United States (NCCAOM - National Certification Commission for Acupuncture and Oriental Medicine).

layout.text: Let's celebrate as we keep TCM regulated by having the Ontario government remove Schedule 5 from BIll 88!
